      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAVANA PERAMA (3) is a last start placegetter in an A3, jumping from this trap and finishing a 3 length third over 500m at this track. Boasts a strong record off this same box, including six wins and 10 placings from 22 starts. Has the ability and looks a key chance. BALLYKILDUFF GEM (1) hit the ground running with a scorching early sectional but ran over late and missed the frame when a 2.75 lengths fourth (29.78) over 500m at this track. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. ANTIGUA BUBBLE (4) caught the eye when posting a sharp 29.48 over 500m at this track three back then has hit the frame in both runs since. Top win three back and rates a key player again. TRAPSTYLE BLUEY (2) followed a moderate fourth at this track two runs ago with another plain effort last time to finish fourth, beaten 9 lengths, in an A2 at this track over 500m (30.57). No surprise to see him back in form.",
